animation raiderWalking
keyframe frame1 of duration 0.15 s
rotate arm_r 75 degrees around x-axis
rotate arm_l -75 degrees around x-axis 
rotate leg_r -75 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_l 75 degrees around x-axis 

keyframe frame2 of duration 0.3 s
rotate arm_r -150 degrees around x-axis
rotate arm_l 150 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_r 150 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_l -150 degrees around x-axis 

keyframe frame3 of duration 0.3 s
rotate arm_r 150 degrees around x-axis
rotate arm_l -150 degrees around x-axis 
rotate leg_r -150 degrees around x-axis
rotate leg_l 150 degrees around x-axis

repeat from frame2

keyframe final of duration 0.5 s
end animation